[SNARLS]

32
00:01:57,942 --> 00:02:01,942
[SILENCE]

33
00:03:05,259 --> 00:03:09,259
[BIRDS CALLING]

34
00:03:34,956 --> 00:03:38,375
[BABIES COOING]

35
00:03:38,376 --> 00:03:43,376
[THUNDER RUMBLES]

36
00:04:17,957 --> 00:04:20,125
[RUSTLING]

37
00:04:20,126 --> 00:04:23,962
[ROARS]

38
